&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Hello &lt;phmention contenteditable="false" class="mprofile" data-id="12974206782"&gt;Habeeb &lt;/phmention&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMPORTANT NOTE:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt; This task has a deadline of Monday, November 26th.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
