&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Topic 3: &lt;a href="https://1stchoiceplumbingheatingandairconditioning.com/traditional-water-heaters/" rel="bookmark"&gt;Choosing Between Tankless and Traditional Water Heaters: What&amp;rsquo;s Best for You?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Email 2: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Topic 1: &lt;a href="https://1stchoiceplumbingheatingandairconditioning.com/importance-of-indoor-air-quality-for-home-office-productivity/" rel="bookmark"&gt;Importance of Indoor Air Quality for Home Office Productivity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Topic 2: &lt;a href="https://1stchoiceplumbingheatingandairconditioning.com/air-balancing-essential-tips-for-a-comfortable-home/" rel="bookmark"&gt;Air Balancing: Essential Tips for a Comfortable Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Topic 3: &lt;a href="https://1stchoiceplumbingheatingandairconditioning.com/why-bathroom-ventilation-is-essential/" rel="bookmark"&gt;Why Bathroom Ventilation is Essential&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
