&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;****&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;The Headline should be similar to the article topics and grab the reader&amp;rsquo;s attention. Be sure to include Preview text as well. Short action, urgent type.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Include an introduction paragraph explaining the purpose for these articles grabbing the reader&amp;rsquo;s attention (moves them closer to their heaven)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Topic 1 - Put the title of the article or topic you&amp;rsquo;re pointing to and a short description or the beginning of the article and a CTA to continue reading.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Topic 2 - Put the title of the article or topic you&amp;rsquo;re pointing to and a short description or the beginning of the article and a CTA to continue reading.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Topic 3 - Put the title of the article or topic you&amp;rsquo;re pointing to and a short description or the beginning of the article and a CTA to continue reading.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;Sign the article from the client&amp;rsquo;s name and add a P.S. section. Include a catchy CTA for the reader to book a call and link to the book a call page for more information and to solve the reader&amp;rsquo;s possible problem.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;The P.S. should NOT be the same for each email. Change up the wording some for each email.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: 400;"&gt;The link to the B.A.C page is here &lt;a href="https://1stchoiceplumbingheatingandairconditioning.com/contact-us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://1stchoiceplumbingheatingandairconditioning.com/contact-us/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
