&lt;p&gt;Hello&amp;nbsp;&lt;phmention contenteditable="false" class="mprofile" data-id="12974206782"&gt;Habeeb&lt;/phmention&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy Friday!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMPORTANT NOTE:&lt;/strong&gt; This task has a deadline of Sunday, November 3rd.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The purpose of this task is to create 4&amp;nbsp; professional content emails that will focus on the reader consuming two articles for Sean at Legendary. These articles are meant to be informative and show readers some of the resources Legendary has to offer.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;B3x is not creating SEO blogs for them as yet so please choose two blog posts per email to leverage on their site: &lt;a href="https://legendaryservice.com/resources/blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Legendary blogs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here is a link to their &lt;a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1VU7nDudZx-gn542q7DJ6gYN80egaMrLla8z3zVLj54g/edit?tab=t.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Beyond the Avatar&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please use the following layout - the same as you've been performing already:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email 1:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 1:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/welcome-to-our-online-home/"&gt;Welcome to Our Online Home!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 2:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/preparing-your-hvac-system-for-libertyvilles-seasonal-shifts/"&gt;Preparing Your HVAC System for Libertyville&amp;rsquo;s Seasonal Shift/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email 2:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 1: &amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/your-ultimate-guide-to-heating-systems-in-libertyville-il/"&gt;Your Ultimate Guide to Heating Systems in Libertyville, IL&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class="inherit" href="https://www.abundance.global/mental-health-first-aid-can-transform-workplace/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;ture&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 2:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/winter-energy-saving-tips-in-illinois/"&gt;Winter Energy Saving Tips in Illinois&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email 3:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 1:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/tips-for-solving-winter-hvac-issues/"&gt;Tips for Solving Winter HVAC Issues&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 2:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/how-to-unclog-a-toilet/"&gt;How to Unclog a Toilet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email 4:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 1: &lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/how-to-fix-a-leaky-faucet/"&gt;How to Fix a Leaky Faucet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 2:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="h4 blog-item__title" href="https://legendaryservice.com/blog/how-to-fix-a-slow-draining-sink/"&gt;How To Fix A Slow Draining Sink&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The 4 emails will be based on the 8 articles above.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;****&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Headline should be similar to the article topics and grab the reader&amp;rsquo;s attention. Be sure to include Preview text as well. Short action, urgent type.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Include an introduction paragraph explaining the purpose for these articles grabbing the reader&amp;rsquo;s attention (moves them closer to their heaven)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Topic 1 - Put the title of the article or topic you&amp;rsquo;re pointing to and a short description or the beginning of the article and a CTA to continue reading.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Topic 2 - Put the title of the article or topic you&amp;rsquo;re pointing to and a short description or the beginning of the article and a CTA to continue reading.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sign the article from the client&amp;rsquo;s name and add a P.S. section. Include a catchy CTA for to encourage the reader to book a call and link to the book-a-call page for more information and to solve the reader&amp;rsquo;s possible problem.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The link to the B.A.C page is here:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://legendaryservice.com/contact/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;https://legendaryservice.com/contact/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;****&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Note:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Emails should be no longer than 4 pages. The content email should be a summary of the article, written to capture the reader&amp;rsquo;s attention and drive them to read the full article and book a call. The P.S. section should be different for each email.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The emails should not look like copy and paste. And please avoid the word &amp;ldquo;delve&amp;rdquo; as we don&amp;rsquo;t want the email to appear as it was written by AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;****&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Does this give you everything you need to start and complete this task?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bill&lt;/p&gt;
