ELL&lt;br /&gt;Founder &amp;amp; Chairman, Breakthrough3x&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;==&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You can also see a sample of the opening/lower thirds in the first 5 seconds of this video: https://youtu.be/Yn5B5mmZIVo?si=YachZIIEWK6-5PaL&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Here's the opening logo: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tOuELx-9x874L9WOcpZAyfkRl6ZSslyg/view?usp=sharing - It should be max of 1-2 seconds; (not the 5 that the file is set at)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Then build in the lower thirds to match; You have our branding guidelines - however because I've seen numerous times where things were off a bit - here they are again:&amp;nbsp;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rOMu28WzRfDNNddibU6hr9TTEL0NwxuN/view?usp=sharing&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;at the end of the video - you would put up a slide or image for the book for someone - that would say on the screen for 5 seconds once Jay and I close it out;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Ideally through the video you do a good job of putting short key words on the screen - adding some B-roll to help break it up; Move in and out on me as I'm speaking (but do it elegantly)&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I can't express enough that I need to get this APPROVED by Jay ABraham's team and they have really, really high standards and it MUST be approved by him and his team; Think of this as the highest quality thing you've ever done for us - that likely should be as close to TV Quality... or Tony Robbins quality...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I'm hoping we also avoid a LOT Of back and forth...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;But if you have questions - do let me know...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Lets make this our best asset for us...&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Dan&lt;/p&gt;
